SAMPLES : gives organisation of saves and resources


############################
###
### Saves
###

2D-SP/saves/
\----save_name/
|    \----mods.yml
|    \----dates.yml
|    \----spacecrafts/
|    |    \----spacecraft_name/
|    |         \----parts/
|    |         |    \----part_name.yml
|    |         \----vectors.yml
|    \----characters.yml
\---
...

mods.yml:
0---------------------------------0
|NAME:LINK                        |
|NAME:LINK                        |
|...                              |
0---------------------------------0
LINK has to point to the https download link. (direct download only available on official website)
     IF one the links is not secure http, the save won't be loaded/displayed.

dates.yml:
0---------------------------------0
|creation_date:DATE               |
|last_modification:DATE           |
0---------------------------------0
DATE format : dd/mm/yyyy/h/m/s

part_name.yml:
0---------------------------------0
|part_resource:PATH               |
|fixed:BOOL                       |
|#if !fixed:                      |
|     position:VECTOR             |
|     direction:VECTOR            |
|     speed:VECTOR                |
|#if fuel tank:                   |
|     fuel_amount:INT             |
|#if engine:                      |
|     thrust_limiter:INT          |
|     status:BOOL                 |
|#if scientific:                  |
|     data:SCIENCE                |
|     status:SCIENCE_STATUS       |
0---------------------------------0
VECTOR format : x/y
BOOL format : TRUE | FALSE
INT format : value
FLOAT format : value
SCIENCE_STATUS format : CLOSED | OPENED
SCIENCE format : text

characters.yml:
0---------------------------------0
|texture:NAME                     |
|sound:NAME                       |
|name:NAME                        |
|status:CHARACTER_STATUS          |
0---------------------------------0
NAME format : text
CHARACTER_STATUS format : HAPPY | AFRAID | NEUTRAL | V_HAPPY | V_AFRAID | LONELY

############################
###
### resources
###

2D-SP/resources/
\----rocket_parts/
|    \----part_textures/
|    |    \----part_name.png
|    \----part_sounds/
|    |    \----part_name.ogg
|    \----part_name.yml
\----planets/
|    \----planet_texture/
|    |    \----planet_texture.png
|    |    \----planet_atmosphere.png
|    \----planet_name.yml
\----background.png
\----physics_constants.yml
\----musics/
|    \----NAME.ogg
\----textures/
|    \----NAME.png
\----characters/
|    \----NAME.ogg
|    \----NAME.png
\---
...

part_name.yml:
0---------------------------------0
|texture:PATH                     |
|mass:FLOAT                       |
|tmp_resistance:FLOAT             |
|g_resistance:FLOAT               |
|#if fuel tank:                   |
|     max_fuel:FLOAT              |
|     fuel_type:FUEL              |
|#if engine:                      |
|     max_fuel:FLOAT              |
|     max_oxydizer:FLOAT          |
|     fuel_type:FUEL              |
|     max_throttle:FLOAT          |
|     sound:PATH                  |
|#if antenna:                     |
|     g_resistance_opened:FLOAT   |
|     tmp_resistance_opened:FLOAT |
|     transmission_power:FLOAT    |
|     transmission_speed:FLOAT    |
|#if command pod:                 |
|     max_crew:INT                |
|     electricity:FLOAT           |
|     sas_power:FLOAT             |
0---------------------------------0
FUEL format : LIQUID | SOLID | L_OXYD | {documentation needed}

planet_name.yml:
0---------------------------------0
|size:FLOAT                       |
|atmosphere:FLOAT                 |
|texture:PATH                     |
|atmosphere_texture:PATH          |
|mass:FLOAT                       |
|atmosphere_levels:LEVELS         |
0---------------------------------0
LEVELS format : top:density/top:density/top:density/top:density/top:density
       example EARTH : 5:1/20:0.7/50:0.4/70:0.2/100:0.1


physics_constants.yml:
0------------------------------------------------------------0
|G:0.00000000000000667                                       |  <-Gravitationnal constant
|h:0.000000000000000000000000000000000626                    |  <-Planck constant
|c:300000000                                                 |  <-light speed
|D:0.00000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000111|  <-Cosmological constant
0------------------------------------------------------------0
constant names can't be changed by mods. Only values my change.

############################
###
### mods
###

2D-SP/mods/
\----mod_name/
|    \----link.txt
|    \----about.yml
|    \----resources
|    |    \----[see resources]
\---
...

link.txt:
0---------------------------------0
|LINK                             |
0---------------------------------0
LINK points to an https link.
     IF link is not a secure http, the mod won't be loaded/displayed.

MODS MUST HAVE THE SAME LICENCE (the MIT licence)

about.yml:
0---------------------------------0
|author:NAME                      |
|creation-date:DATE               |
|description:TEXT                 |
0---------------------------------0


See CREATING_MODS for more details.